    <url>/2023/11/20/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BAblog/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="2023-11-20"><a href="#2023-11-20" class="headerlink" title="2023&#x2F;11&#x2F;20"></a>2023&#x2F;11&#x2F;20</h1><p>参考博客：</p><figure class="highlight sas"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sas">https://blog.csdn.net/a3212/article/details/77099492?ops_request_misc=<span class="hljs-variable">&amp;request_id</span>=<span class="hljs-variable">&amp;biz_id</span>=102<span class="hljs-variable">&amp;utm_term</span>=hexo<span class="hljs-title function_">%E6</span>%90<span class="hljs-title function_">%AD</span><span class="hljs-title function_">%E5</span><span class="hljs-title function_">%BB</span><span class="hljs-title function_">%BA</span><span class="hljs-title function_">%E4</span><span class="hljs-title function_">%B8</span><span class="hljs-title function_">%AA</span><span class="hljs-title function_">%E4</span><span class="hljs-title function_">%BA</span><span class="hljs-title function_">%BA</span><span class="hljs-title function_">%E5</span>%8D%9A<span class="hljs-title function_">%E5</span><span class="hljs-title function_">%AE</span><span class="hljs-title function_">%A2</span><span class="hljs-variable">&amp;utm_medium</span>=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~blog~sobaiduweb~default-0-77099492.nonecase<span class="hljs-variable">&amp;spm</span>=1018.2226.3001.4450<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-准备环境"><a href="#1-准备环境" class="headerlink" title="1.  准备环境"></a>1.  准备环境</h3><blockquote><p>node.js  ——  v14.16.0</p><p>git   ——   git version 2.42.0.windows.2</p><p>github  ——  注册账号</p></blockquote><h3 id="2-安装hexo"><a href="#2-安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装hexo"></a>2. 安装hexo</h3><p><strong>遇到问题： npm install hexo报错</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git报错bash: npm: <span class="hljs-built_in">command</span> not found<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><ul><li><p>去看高级系统设置里面的用户和系统变量里面的路径</p></li><li><p>看nodejs里面node_cache  node_global系统路径是否正确</p></li><li><p>npm config set cache&#x2F;prefix 是否&#x3D;对应路径(D:node_cache  node_global)</p><p><strong>还不行就重新下载node.js，看b站收藏夹视频</strong></p></li></ul></blockquote><h4 id="2-1-D盘创建Hexo-CSDN，右键以git-bash打开"><a href="#2-1-D盘创建Hexo-CSDN，右键以git-bash打开" class="headerlink" title="2.1  D盘创建Hexo_CSDN，右键以git bash打开"></a>2.1  D盘创建Hexo_CSDN，右键以git bash打开</h4><p>执行以下命令，中间的报错不管：</p><figure class="highlight coffeescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs coffeescript"><span class="hljs-built_in">npm</span> i -g hexo  (<span class="hljs-built_in">npm</span>报错看上面)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">npm</span> install -g hexo-cli<br>可输入 hexo -v查看是否已经安装好<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-2-执行hexo命令创建页面"><a href="#2-2-执行hexo命令创建页面" class="headerlink" title="2.2 执行hexo命令创建页面"></a>2.2 执行hexo命令创建页面</h4><p>执行如下命令：</p><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pgsql">hexo init  <span class="hljs-comment">--初始化hexo环境,这时会在目录下自动生成hexo的文件</span><br><br>npm install <span class="hljs-comment">--安装npm依赖包</span><br><br>hexo generate <span class="hljs-comment">--生成静态页面</span><br><br>hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">server</span> <span class="hljs-comment">--生成本地服务</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>遇到问题 hexo  init报错：</strong>&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>​原因是当前文件路径下D&#x2F;Hexo_CSDN文件夹不为空，而此命令必须运行在空文件夹下，故新建D:\Hexo_CSDN\CSDNblog，进入此目录重新运行上述命令。</p><h3 id="3-将本地博客发布到网络上"><a href="#3-将本地博客发布到网络上" class="headerlink" title="3.  将本地博客发布到网络上"></a>3.  将本地博客发布到网络上</h3><h4 id="3-1-hexo-deploy报错："><a href="#3-1-hexo-deploy报错：" class="headerlink" title="3.1  hexo deploy报错："></a>3.1  hexo deploy报错：</h4><figure class="highlight vbnet"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs vbnet"><span class="hljs-symbol">fatal:</span> unable <span class="hljs-keyword">to</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">auto</span>-detect email address (got <span class="hljs-comment">&#x27;淅沥@LAPTOPHL.(none)&#x27;)</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行下面两条命令前要先执行git init ，因为是新仓库：</p><figure class="highlight lua"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs lua">git <span class="hljs-built_in">config</span> <span class="hljs-comment">--global user.name your_name</span><br>git <span class="hljs-built_in">config</span> <span class="hljs-comment">--global user.email your_email</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3-2-hexo-d报错："><a href="#3-2-hexo-d报错：" class="headerlink" title="3.2  hexo d报错："></a>3.2  hexo d报错：</h4><p>执行：</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus"><span class="hljs-comment">//取消https代理</span><br>git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> <span class="hljs-attr">--unset</span> https<span class="hljs-selector-class">.proxy</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//取消http代理</span><br>git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> <span class="hljs-attr">--unset</span> http.proxy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-尝试访问"><a href="#4-尝试访问" class="headerlink" title="4.  尝试访问"></a>4.  尝试访问</h3><p>公共网址：<a href="https://subai-01.github.io/">https://SuBai-01.github.io/</a></p><h3 id="5-其它"><a href="#5-其它" class="headerlink" title="5.  其它"></a>5.  其它</h3><p>挑选博客theme：<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">https://hexo.io/themes/</a></p><p>fluid官方说明：<a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid</a></p><p>fluid用户手册：<a href="https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/guide">https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/guide</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
